title: ICSI CS Executive & Professional December 2025 Admit Cards Released!
content:
# ICSI CS Executive & Professional December 2025 Admit Cards Released!

Ek important update hai Company Secretary aspirants ke liye! The Institute of Company Secretaries of India (ICSI) ne CS Executive aur Professional December 2025 examinations ke admit cards release kar diye hain. Yeh admit cards 12 December 2025 ko jaari kiye gaye hain.

*   **What:** CS Executive and CS Professional December 2025 session ke liye admit cards ab available hain.
*   **When:** Admit cards 12 December 2025 ko release kiye gaye hain.
*   **Exam Dates:** The examinations are scheduled to be held from December 22 to December 29, 2025.
*   **How to Download:** Candidates can download their admit cards from the official ICSI website by logging in with their 17-digit registration number.
*   **Important:** Admit card ka printed copy aur ek valid government-issued photo ID exam hall mein carry karna mandatory hai.

## Read the Official Document
*   [Download the Official Notification/Circular here](https://www.icsi.edu/)

*Published on: 13 December 2025*
